data.description: A conventional hypodermic 3-parts syringe made of medical grade polypropylene and isoprene latex-free rubber and natural rubber. It is sterilized with Ethylene Oxide (EO). The syringe comes in different presentations such as Luer Lock and Luer Slip Tips, with and without needle, latex and latex-free gasket. It also has customizable graduation including logo and some sizes with centric and excentric luer tips. It has clear graduation printing technology, high transparency barrel, smooth sliding, and smooth surface.
